      <title>特朗普袭击乌克兰的Zelenskiy时，有什么危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/after-trump-zelenskiy-talks-collapse-what-s-at-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）长期表示，他将迅速结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争。为了达成协议，美国已经与克里姆林宫官员进行了直接讨论，乌克兰和欧洲大国在谈判中占据一席之地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/after-trump-zelenskiy-talks-collapse-what-s-at-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 12:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
